Functional requierments:
-   secure sensor data in service provider servers
-   live sensor data access
-   old sensor data access
-   monitoring website
-   

Non-functional requierments:
-   RPC Thrift connection between Central and Service provider
-   Postgres DB  for sensor data protection
-   system redundancy
-   possible high system performance
-   sensors can basic GETs 
-   sensors communucation with central via UDP/MQTT
-   webserver for central
-   IPs Ports,Type of sensor has to be logged
-   system self check - functional test
-   performance test
-   debug with logfiles
